.com/taylorswift13?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">泰勒斯威夫特13 的推文</a><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>《The Tortured Poets Department》将标志着泰勒·斯威夫特的第 11 张录音室专辑。在此之前，她于 2022 年发行了唱片《Midnights》，最近又重新录制了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-speak-now-taylors-version-during-nashville-show-3440063">《Speak Now》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">《1989》</a> 。这张专辑已确认由 Post Malone 和 Florence + The Machine 主演。</p><p>在格莱美奖的其他地方，泰勒·斯威夫特凭借《Midnights》荣获年度专辑奖，这是她第四次获得该奖项。凭借这一胜利，斯威夫特现在成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-wins-record-setting-fourth-album-of-the-year-at-2024-grammys-3582336">年度最佳专辑奖项的历史领先者，创下了新纪录</a>。她此前与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">史蒂夫·旺德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-simon">保罗·西蒙</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-sinatra">弗兰克·西纳特拉</a>并列三场胜利。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-official-tracklist-for-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583090">《这是泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的《The Tortured Poets Department》的官方曲目列表》一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
